node.title: A judge has dismissed criminal charges in an outbreak at a home for veterans in Massachusetts.
node.alt: The emergency room at Mount Sinai South Nassau in Oceanside, N.Y., will have to handle patients from the Long Beach Emergency Department during the closure.
node.description: The judge wrote that two former administrators at the Soldiersâ€™ Home in Holyoke, Mass., could not be held legally responsible because the veterans in the case had been exposed before two units at the home were merged.
